{"tid":2377870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我登國防部出咗聲明撐台灣冇人講？","createTime":"2021-01-24T03:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T10:09:25.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f34e71c78f8e57ba55e01ad4780eeb84533ded53","tid":2377870,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:51:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/prc-military-pressure-against-taiwan-threatens-regional-peace-and-stability/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fprc-military-pressure-against-taiwan-threatens-regional-peace-and-stability%2F%3F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TapMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=4a51b31d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/prc-military-pressure-against-taiwan-threatens-regional-peace-and-stability/?</a><br />\n<br />\nPRC Military Pressure Against Taiwan Threatens Regional Peace and Stability<br />\nPRESS RELEASE<br />\n<br />\nNED PRICE, DEPARTMENT SPOKESPERSON<br />\n<br />\nThe United States notes with concern the pattern of ongoing PRC attempts to intimidate its neighbors, including Taiwan. We urge Beijing to cease its military, diplomatic, and economic pressure against Taiwan and instead engage in meaningful dialogue with Taiwan&rsquo;s democratically elected representatives.<br />\n<br />\nWe will stand with friends and allies to advance our shared prosperity, security, and values in the Indo-Pacific region &mdash; and that includes deepening our ties with democratic Taiwan. The United States will continue to support a peaceful resolution of cross-strait issues, consistent with the wishes and best interests of the people on Taiwan. The United States maintains its longstanding commitments as outlined in the Three Communiqu&eacute;s, the Taiwan Relations Act, and the Six Assurances. We will continue to assist Taiwan in maintaining a sufficient self-defense capability. Our commitment to Taiwan is rock-solid and contributes to the maintenance of peace and stability across the Taiwan Strait and within the region.<br />\n<br />\n中國對台灣的軍事壓力破壞地區和平與穩定<br />\n新聞稿<br />\n<br />\n NED PRICE，部門發言人<br />\n<br />\n美國關切地注意到，中國不斷企圖恐嚇包括台灣在內的鄰國。 我們敦促北京停止對台灣的軍事，外交和經濟壓力，而應與台灣民選代表進行有意義的對話。<br />\n<br />\n我們將與朋友和盟友站在一起，以促進我們在印度太平洋地區的共同繁榮，安全和價值觀，其中包括加深我們與民主台灣的聯繫。 美國將繼續按照台灣人民的願望和最大利益，以和平方式解決兩岸問題。 美國恪守《三個公報》，《台灣關係法》和《六項保證》所概述的長期承諾。 我們將繼續協助台灣保持足夠的自衛能力。 我們對台灣的承諾堅定不移，為維護台灣海峽及整個地區的和平與穩定作出了貢獻。"},{"pid":"e26f9b52233c89e34344e97a8d1b32add03cf09f","tid":2377870,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fa8294672de034628ee8192183afc37d94b037","tid":2377870,"uid":290393,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"e26f9b52233c89e34344e97a8d1b32add03cf09f","tid":2377870,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"又係講左當做左<br />\n<br />\n完全睇到以前奧巴馬果個風格"},{"pid":"4ebc3eed9928b65ea1b8c52f1a3b468722b7431e","tid":2377870,"uid":61032,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"聲明黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd45d01e1464cca4ca49922a2961b902ee26ea","tid":2377870,"uid":169079,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"d14db4179e720ecea312a1db595b765ae4def072","tid":2377870,"uid":266654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"潛台詞<br />\n<br />\n登：嗱，我而家相信對話可以解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你知點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"